Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.36,0:00:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck do you have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to hide it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.82,0:00:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I actually wanted was \NHideyoshi's picture, not your{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel my wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your payback for always being a bitch to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I request a mock-ESB!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission to summon, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Being...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Being...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon! Summon! Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon! Summon! Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon! Summon!!!!!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Approval denied!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't control the ESB field!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disaster always strikes unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The password?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah, Hideyoshi in a waitress outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me glad to be alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a picture of him changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll cost you double, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you cut me a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already living off salt water this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy one, get one free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so much work...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another layer of security?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pass is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost pissed my pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we have a problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be a problem with the summoning system.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you ever shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you do this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I always the number one suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better fess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your Being's the only one that's acting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the system is unstable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to summon mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A grown-up version, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji, no looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's what Himeji will look like in a few years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so... well-developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm going to be too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like her master, completely undev-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit, a Frankensteiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can get a nude shot if I do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.49,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're brilliant, Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.36,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skeletal frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it sounded like a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if I back up some more...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll summon mine as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't, Mr. Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't mistaken about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is obviously a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an error in the system!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll try too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabulous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look so cute together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Voyeur?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's malfunctioning...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does yours look like, Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, show us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is mine the odd one out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher's Beings were being held near the core,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they've completely frozen. They can't be summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the students' Beings are out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't access the server room's security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that we can't open the \Ndoors. There's no way to fix the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't we turn off the power to the system?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll keep running for at least a month with the UPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we'd have to bruteforce our way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're holding a presentation about the security system tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that if there's a hole in the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we put the idiot to work for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to fix what, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Beings of Punishment Inspectors run under a different system,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they're not affected by the \Nmalfunction like the other students'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why Akihisa's Being was acting differently from ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't summon it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you tried to summon it in a corrupted Instructor Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have your own field, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this iron bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go into the server room with your Being and connect the cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I'll shut off the security system from the terminal and open the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh. This plan wouldn't work without a Being that can manipulate physical space.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:10:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Being can't go through walls, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an AC vent that's used for system cooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Being should be small enough to pass through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he supposed to control it without being able to see where it's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A video camera and a transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you give these to your Being, you'll be able to see the inside of the vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so smart, Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you have those on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you use them for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat him like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually a great guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a little, well, really perverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.70,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even said anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:32.27,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Akihisa's his VIP customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The iron bracelet can only create a short-range summoning field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to control your Being from right outside the server room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll direct you from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Being has entered the vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Course clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's under special observation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he's a problem child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the only one who can use the iron bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right at 3 meters ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn left at the first cross road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a friggin' maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so confusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's another brand of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, I'm feeling numb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing points!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a poison swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell would you do that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's another brand of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll avoid the danger zones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right at the next corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoned Beings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Berserk Beings have appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it stop, Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't control him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji! Hideyoshi! Minori! Himeji! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who were KIA must receive supplementary lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was the lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll resume the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take the recovery exam and replenish your points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll have to get a really high \Nscore to survive those attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me to help you study?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me to help you study?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A private lesson with you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure pick up stuff like {\i1}that{\i0} quickly, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless unless it shows immediate results.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then I have a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can get easy points with these easy problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda cheating, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa's power level is off the charts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing great, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you get wrong, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Taika Reform was in 645!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you possibly forget that after what happened a little while ago!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I got confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, he's leveled up quite a bit, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be able to deal with the enemy attacks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resume mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so gonna beat it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a left at that crossroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poison swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it hurts no matter how high your level is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm not a lab rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a right when you reach the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you touch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bad habit of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm not gonna lose again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchiya's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The subject is history!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:16:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's only good at health, so \Nthere's no way he can beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There stood a poison swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.39,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who were KIA must receive supplementary lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Beings lost on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resistance is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a disconnected cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wooden Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phase synchronization detected in the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Being is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sissy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be just your Being, but I won't let anyone else have it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow it to touch anyone's except mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supplementary lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Himeji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii! You won't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so close...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should pull him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think teachers should be forcing students to do-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have enough points left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The difference in strength is too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Difference in points doesn't always equal a difference in strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how my Being got stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji, take the recovery exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to take the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your points increase, his \Nchances will be less than zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please grade this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki Himeji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did good, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system is beginning to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the problem's solved for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who were KIA must receive supplementary lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking so blue for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My points!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't whine about a couple of points.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go take your supplementary lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a pretty big gamble letting the class F kids handle this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm glad it worked out in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.07,0:23:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see it as a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.78,0:23:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to deal with idiots, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.84,0:23:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question 9:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We use the unit "cup" to measure the bust size of women.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Describe the size of a basic A cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.11,0:23:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Kiss and Bust and Ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be on your test.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.05,0:02:07.30,Anime Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(640,110)\bord8\shad0\be1\blur2\3c&HE07EFF&}Idiots and Tests and Summoned Beings
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.05,0:02:07.30,Anime Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(640,110)\bord6\shad0\3c&HFFFFFF&}Idiots and Tests and Summoned Beings
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.05,0:02:07.30,Anime Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(639,109)\be1}Idiots and Tests and Summoned Beings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:53.04,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\c&HF1DEEB&}Just who are we letting grow up on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:11.22,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\c&HFFF3BA&}Meeting someone else is the easy way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:13.89,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\c&HEBD5FE&}I knew what I would say before they even asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:16.44,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\c&HB1FFB2&}Do I look lovestruck enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.65,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\c&HC9E4FF&}I'm not gonna lose my cool, love's at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:21.69,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\c&HCAC7FF&}Study! Study! Study! It keeps me up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:24.32,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\c&HFFC9EB&}I've got a genius inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.91,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\c&HA0E6FF&}It'd be great if my dreams came true
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.11,0:02:29.16,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\c&HD6C3CB&}because I don't care about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:31.74,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\c&HD5CDFF&}Perfect area complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.45,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\c&HCDFFDC&}I'll be waiting for you!
